---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="GLADR – Deine Steuererstattung. Automatisch."
  description="Als Student fährst du jedes Semester hunderte Kilometer. Das Finanzamt erstattet dir das – GLADR trackt es automatisch."
>

  <!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
  <section class="bg-midnight min-h-screen flex items-center relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-midnight via-midnight to-[#1a2744] pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-1/4 right-1/3 w-[32rem] h-[32rem] bg-emerald/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/4 w-64 h-64 bg-indigo/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 sm:py-32 w-full">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">

        <!-- Left: Text -->
        <div>
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/10 text-white/70 text-sm font-inter px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-8 border border-white/10">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald animate-pulse"></span>
            Coming Soon &middot; iOS &amp; Android
          </div>

          <h1 class="font-grotesk font-bold text-5xl sm:text-6xl text-white leading-[1.1] mb-6">
            Deine<br />
            Steuererstattung.<br />
            <span class="text-emerald">Automatisch.</span>
          </h1>

          <p class="font-inter text-lg text-white/60 leading-relaxed mb-10">
            Als Student fährst du jedes Semester hunderte Kilometer zur Uni,
            Bibliothek und zu Lerngruppen. Das Finanzamt erstattet dir das&nbsp;—
            die meisten wissen es nur nicht.
          </p>

          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <a
              href="#wie-es-funktioniert"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-emerald text-midnight font-grotesk font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-emerald/90 transition-colors text-base"
            >
              Wie es funktioniert
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none">
                <path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
            <a
              href="#das-problem"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 border border-white/20 text-white/70 font-inter px-8 py-4 rounded-xl hover:border-white/40 hover:text-white transition-colors text-base"
            >
              Mehr erfahren
            </a>
          </div>

          <!-- Stats -->
          <div class="mt-14 grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 border-t border-white/10 pt-10">
            <div>
              <div class="font-grotesk font-bold text-2xl text-white mb-1">450&nbsp;€</div>
              <div class="font-inter text-xs text-white/40">Ø pro Jahr</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-grotesk font-bold text-2xl text-white mb-1">§&nbsp;9</div>
              <div class="font-inter text-xs text-white/40">EStG</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-grotesk font-bold text-2xl text-white mb-1">0,38&nbsp;€</div>
              <div class="font-inter text-xs text-white/40">pro km</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: Phone Mockup -->
        <div class="hidden lg:flex justify-center items-center">
          <div class="relative">
            <!-- Glow behind phone -->
            <div class="absolute -inset-8 bg-emerald/10 rounded-[5rem] blur-3xl"></div>
            <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-indigo/5 rounded-[4rem] blur-2xl"></div>

            <!-- Phone frame -->
            <div class="relative w-[280px] h-[580px] bg-[#0d1526] rounded-[3rem] border border-white/10 shadow-2xl overflow-hidden">

              <!-- Dynamic island -->
              <div class="absolute top-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-28 h-7 bg-black rounded-full z-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-white/20"></div>
                <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-white/10 border border-white/20"></div>
              </div>

              <!-- Screen content -->
              <div class="pt-16 px-5 pb-6 h-full flex flex-col">

                <!-- App header -->
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-5">
                  <div>
                    <div class="font-grotesk font-bold text-white text-base">GLADR</div>
                    <div class="font-inter text-white/30 text-xs">Steuerjahr 2026</div>
                  </div>
                  <!-- Geofence active badge -->
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-emerald/15 border border-emerald/30 rounded-full px-3 py-1">
                    <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald"></span>
                    <span class="font-inter text-emerald text-xs">Aktiv</span>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Main stat card -->
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald/20 to-emerald/5 border border-emerald/20 rounded-2xl p-4 mb-5">
                  <div class="font-inter text-white/50 text-xs mb-1">Erstattungspotenzial</div>
                  <div class="font-grotesk font-bold text-4xl text-emerald mb-1">387,50&nbsp;€</div>
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
                    <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none">
                      <path d="M2 8l4-4 4 4" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                    </svg>
                    <span class="font-inter text-emerald/70 text-xs">+23,00&nbsp;€ diese Woche</span>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Trip list -->
                <div class="font-inter text-white/30 text-xs mb-3 uppercase tracking-wider">Letzte Fahrten</div>
                <div class="space-y-2.5 flex-1">

                  <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-3 flex items-center gap-3">
                    <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-emerald/15 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                      <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none">
                        <path d="M7 1C4.79 1 3 2.79 3 5c0 3 4 8 4 8s4-5 4-8c0-2.21-1.79-4-4-4z" fill="#10B981"/>
                        <circle cx="7" cy="5" r="1.5" fill="#0d1526"/>
                      </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
                      <div class="font-inter text-white text-xs font-medium">Uni Köln</div>
                      <div class="font-inter text-white/30 text-xs">Heute · 38 km</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="font-grotesk font-semibold text-emerald text-sm">+14,44&nbsp;€</div>
                  </div>

                  <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-3 flex items-center gap-3">
                    <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-indigo/15 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                      <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none">
                        <rect x="2" y="3" width="10" height="8" rx="1.5" stroke="#6366F1" stroke-width="1.2"/>
                        <path d="M4 3V2.5a.5.5 0 011 0V3M9 3V2.5a.5.5 0 011 0V3" stroke="#6366F1" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                        <path d="M4.5 7h5M4.5 9h3" stroke="#6366F1" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                      </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
                      <div class="font-inter text-white text-xs font-medium">Stadtbibliothek</div>
                      <div class="font-inter text-white/30 text-xs">Gestern · 12 km</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="font-grotesk font-semibold text-white/50 text-sm">+3,60&nbsp;€</div>
                  </div>

                  <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-3 flex items-center gap-3">
                    <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-white/8 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                      <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none">
                        <circle cx="4" cy="5" r="1.5" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.2"/>
                        <circle cx="10" cy="5" r="1.5" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.2"/>
                        <circle cx="7" cy="9" r="1.5" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.2"/>
                        <path d="M5.5 5h3M5 6l-1 2.5M9 6l1 2.5" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                      </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
                      <div class="font-inter text-white text-xs font-medium">Lerngruppe</div>
                      <div class="font-inter text-white/30 text-xs">Mo · 18 km</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="font-grotesk font-semibold text-white/50 text-sm">+5,40&nbsp;€</div>
                  </div>

                </div>

                <!-- Bottom nav bar -->
                <div class="flex justify-around items-center pt-4 border-t border-white/8 mt-3">
                  <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-1">
                    <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none">
                      <rect x="2" y="9" width="4" height="7" rx="1" fill="#10B981"/>
                      <rect x="7" y="5" width="4" height="11" rx="1" fill="#10B981" opacity="0.5"/>
                      <rect x="12" y="2" width="4" height="14" rx="1" fill="#10B981" opacity="0.3"/>
                    </svg>
                    <div class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-emerald"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-1">
                    <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none">
                      <path d="M9 2L3 7h2v7h3v-4h2v4h3V7h2L9 2z" fill="#475569"/>
                    </svg>
                    <div class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-transparent"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-1">
                    <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none">
                      <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="3" stroke="#475569" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                      <path d="M3 16c0-3.31 2.69-6 6-6s6 2.69 6 6" stroke="#475569" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                    </svg>
                    <div class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-transparent"></div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Home indicator -->
                <div class="flex justify-center mt-3">
                  <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-white/20 rounded-full"></div>
                </div>

              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== DAS PROBLEM ===== -->
  <section id="das-problem" class="bg-background py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mb-16">
        <p class="font-inter text-sm font-medium text-emerald uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Das Problem</p>
        <h2 class="font-grotesk font-bold text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-midnight leading-tight mb-6">
          450&nbsp;€ pro Jahr.<br />Meistens ungenutzt.
        </h2>
        <p class="font-inter text-lg text-midnight/60 leading-relaxed">
          Das Steuerrecht gibt Studierenden das Recht auf diese Erstattungen&nbsp;— aber kaum jemand
          behält den Überblick über seine Fahrten. GLADR erledigt das automatisch.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-card border border-border p-7 group hover:border-emerald/30 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-emerald/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
              <path d="M12 3C8.13 3 5 6.13 5 10c0 5.25 7 13 7 13s7-7.75 7-13c0-3.87-3.13-7-7-7z" fill="#10B981" opacity="0.2"/>
              <path d="M12 3C8.13 3 5 6.13 5 10c0 5.25 7 13 7 13s7-7.75 7-13c0-3.87-3.13-7-7-7z" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.5"/>
              <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="2.5" fill="#10B981"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="font-grotesk font-bold text-3xl text-midnight mb-1">0,38&nbsp;€<span class="text-lg font-medium text-midnight/40">/km</span></div>
          <div class="font-inter font-semibold text-midnight mb-3">Entfernungspauschale</div>
          <p class="font-inter text-sm text-midnight/55 leading-relaxed">
            Für jeden Kilometer zwischen Wohnort und Uni. Hin- und Rückweg, für jeden Studientag.
            Geregelt in §&nbsp;9 Abs.&nbsp;1 Nr.&nbsp;4 EStG.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-card border border-border p-7 group hover:border-indigo/30 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-indigo/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
              <rect x="3" y="6" width="18" height="13" rx="2.5" fill="#6366F1" opacity="0.15"/>
              <rect x="3" y="6" width="18" height="13" rx="2.5" stroke="#6366F1" stroke-width="1.5"/>
              <path d="M8 6V4.5a.5.5 0 011 0V6M15 6V4.5a.5.5 0 011 0V6" stroke="#6366F1" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <path d="M3 10h18" stroke="#6366F1" stroke-width="1.5"/>
              <path d="M7 14h3M14 14h3M7 17h2" stroke="#6366F1" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="font-grotesk font-bold text-3xl text-midnight mb-1">0,30&nbsp;€<span class="text-lg font-medium text-midnight/40">/km</span></div>
          <div class="font-inter font-semibold text-midnight mb-3">Reisekosten</div>
          <p class="font-inter text-sm text-midnight/55 leading-relaxed">
            Für Fahrten zur Bibliothek, zu Lerngruppen oder Exkursionen. Hin- und
            Rückweg werden automatisch erfasst.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-card border border-border p-7 group hover:border-error/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-error/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
              <path d="M12 3L4 8v5c0 4.41 3.41 8.53 8 9.54C16.59 21.53 20 17.41 20 13V8L12 3z" fill="#E11D48" opacity="0.15"/>
              <path d="M12 3L4 8v5c0 4.41 3.41 8.53 8 9.54C16.59 21.53 20 17.41 20 13V8L12 3z" stroke="#E11D48" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="#E11D48" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="font-grotesk font-bold text-3xl text-midnight mb-1">14–28&nbsp;€<span class="text-lg font-medium text-midnight/40">/Tag</span></div>
          <div class="font-inter font-semibold text-midnight mb-3">Verpflegungspauschale</div>
          <p class="font-inter text-sm text-midnight/55 leading-relaxed">
            Bei Fahrten über 8 Stunden: 14&nbsp;€. Bei Fahrten über 24 Stunden: 28&nbsp;€.
            Nur für Reisefahrten, nicht Pendeln.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="font-inter text-sm text-midnight/40 mt-10 text-center italic">
        „Das Gesetz gibt dir das Recht&nbsp;— du musst es nur einfordern."
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== WIE ES FUNKTIONIERT ===== -->
  <section id="wie-es-funktioniert" class="bg-midnight py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mb-20">
        <p class="font-inter text-sm font-medium text-emerald uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">So funktioniert es</p>
        <h2 class="font-grotesk font-bold text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-white leading-tight mb-6">
          Einmal einrichten.<br />
          <span class="text-emerald">Automatisch tracken.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="font-inter text-lg text-white/55 leading-relaxed">
          Kein manuelles Eintragen. Kein vergessener Fahrtweg.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Steps -->
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8 relative">
        <!-- Connecting line (desktop) -->
        <div class="hidden sm:block absolute top-10 left-[calc(16.66%+20px)] right-[calc(16.66%+20px)] h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/10 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>

        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-start">
          <div class="relative mb-6">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald/20 to-emerald/5 border border-emerald/20 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none">
                <!-- Phone with location pin -->
                <rect x="10" y="4" width="16" height="28" rx="3" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                <path d="M15 4V3M21 4V3" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                <circle cx="18" cy="30" r="1" fill="#10B981"/>
                <path d="M18 13C15.79 13 14 14.79 14 17c0 3.5 4 7 4 7s4-3.5 4-7c0-2.21-1.79-4-4-4z" fill="#10B981" opacity="0.4"/>
                <circle cx="18" cy="17" r="1.5" fill="#10B981"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-emerald flex items-center justify-center font-grotesk font-bold text-midnight text-sm">1</div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-grotesk font-bold text-xl text-white mb-3">App installieren</h3>
          <p class="font-inter text-white/55 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Trag einmal deinen Wohnort und deine Uni ein. GLADR richtet die Geofence-Zonen
            automatisch ein. Das war's.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-start">
          <div class="relative mb-6">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo/20 to-indigo/5 border border-indigo/20 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none">
                <!-- Radar / signal waves -->
                <circle cx="18" cy="20" r="3" fill="#6366F1"/>
                <path d="M12 20c0-3.31 2.69-6 6-6s6 2.69 6 6" stroke="#6366F1" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.7"/>
                <path d="M8 20c0-5.52 4.48-10 10-10s10 4.48 10 10" stroke="#6366F1" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.4"/>
                <path d="M4 20c0-7.73 6.27-14 14-14s14 6.27 14 14" stroke="#6366F1" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.2"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-indigo-500 flex items-center justify-center font-grotesk font-bold text-white text-sm">2</div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-grotesk font-bold text-xl text-white mb-3">Automatisch tracken</h3>
          <p class="font-inter text-white/55 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            GPS-Geofencing erkennt, wann du losfährst und ankommst. Fahrten werden
            im Hintergrund erfasst und kategorisiert — ohne dass du etwas tun musst.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-start">
          <div class="relative mb-6">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-white/10 to-white/5 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none">
                <!-- Document with checkmark + bar chart -->
                <rect x="8" y="4" width="20" height="28" rx="2.5" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.6"/>
                <path d="M13 14h10M13 18h10M13 22h6" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.4"/>
                <path d="M13 10h10" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                <path d="M22 24l-3 3-2-2" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-white/20 border border-white/30 flex items-center justify-center font-grotesk font-bold text-white text-sm">3</div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-grotesk font-bold text-xl text-white mb-3">Fertige Übersicht</h3>
          <p class="font-inter text-white/55 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Am Jahresende: vollständige Auflistung aller Fahrten, Kilometer und
            Steuerbeträge — genau so, wie das Finanzamt es braucht.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== DAS GESETZ ===== -->
  <section class="bg-background py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mb-16">
        <p class="font-inter text-sm font-medium text-emerald uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Rechtliche Grundlage</p>
        <h2 class="font-grotesk font-bold text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-midnight leading-tight mb-6">
          Nicht erfunden.<br />Gesetzlich geregelt.
        </h2>
        <p class="font-inter text-lg text-midnight/60 leading-relaxed">
          GLADR berechnet nichts dazu. Wir wenden nur an, was das Einkommensteuergesetz
          ohnehin vorsieht.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-card border border-border p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-200">
          <div class="inline-block font-grotesk font-semibold text-xs text-emerald mb-4 bg-emerald/10 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">§ 9 Abs. 1 Satz 3 Nr. 4 EStG</div>
          <h3 class="font-grotesk font-bold text-xl text-midnight mb-4">Entfernungspauschale</h3>
          <p class="font-inter text-midnight/60 leading-relaxed mb-5">
            Werbungskosten für Fahrten zwischen Wohnung und erster Tätigkeitsstätte
            (für Studierende: der Hauptcampus). 0,38&nbsp;€ pro Entfernungskilometer,
            für jeden Anwesenheitstag.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-background rounded-xl p-4 font-inter text-sm">
            <div class="text-midnight/40 mb-1 text-xs uppercase tracking-wide">Beispiel</div>
            <div class="text-midnight/70">15 km × 0,38&nbsp;€ × 180 Tage</div>
            <div class="font-grotesk font-bold text-2xl text-midnight mt-1">= 1.026&nbsp;€</div>
          </div>
        </div>

